                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950416-79-defend876 t17950416-79-punish456"></join>
               Fined one shilling
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
